Chicken cutlet is a Taiwanese street food made with chicken breast or chicken thigh that is thinly sliced, coated in flour or sweet potato starch, and deep-fried. Chicken cutlet is typically cut into square or rectangular shapes and can be served with rice, noodles, or vegetables.

Chicken cutlet is crispy on the outside and juicy on the inside, making it a popular snack among Taiwanese people. Chicken cutlet can also be served as a main course with sauce, vegetables, and rice, making it a nutritious meal.

Here are some additional information about chicken cutlet:

  • Chicken cutlet is typically sold at night markets or snack shops.

  • Chicken cutlet can be served with a variety of sauces, such as ketchup, chili sauce, mayonnaise, or sweet and spicy sauce.

  • Chicken cutlet can be served with a variety of vegetables, such as lettuce, onions, bell peppers, or corn.

  • Chicken cutlet can be served as a main course with sauce, vegetables, and rice.

If you ever have the chance to visit Taiwan, be sure to try chicken cutlet. It is a delicious and nutritious street food.

items.name: Sun]flower
items.description:
Hi!

Sorry for the lack of news but I have been doing lots and lots of training so I can understand better SDXL new architecture. I'm on it but for now I wanted to present (and after 2 weeks of heavy tunning) Sun]flower, a new SDXL LORA and my very first SDXL Style LORA.


Sun]flower is a SDXL LORA that has certain sunflower plant aesthetics and can be used in a lot of different ways. I have tested it in WebUI and ComfyUI... I'm not sure yet which one I liked most but the sample images I put here (except 2) are from ComfyUI, in the next days I will upload some Webui Sample images too.



- If you want to know how to prompt please refer to the sample images.

- Trigger is snfw3r

- Recommended weight is 1 but if you feel there are too much sunflower in the scene use 0.6 onwards. Depends a lot on the concept and seed.
- Resolution recommended 1024x1024 or 1024x768/1024x1456 and even 512x768 or 768x768. Resolution will guide too the prompt, remember this.

- You can guide more the AI towards the style using "3d render", "drawing", etc. Remember that now SDXL will follow much better prompt.

- This LORA is good for almost anything except probably realistic but try to maintain prompts simple as possible and focus on what you want to see.

- This LORA was trained in more than 1 style so it can transfer to concept, illustration, 3D render, etc. Guide it with your prompt.

- This LORA wasn't testted on finetunned XL Dreambooth models because I wanted to see the inner strenght of it. Feel free to test it wherever you want.

In the case you want my workflow:
https://huggingface.co/datasets/davizca87/C01nWorkflow/tree/main <- LOAD it via Json file in Comfyui



And that's all. As always, eternal gratitude for all people giving feedback here, in Discord and of course supporting us in Patreon!

Remember we are in SDXL territory and I'm not as versed as in SD 1.5 so feeback, positive or negative is very much welcome.

NOTE: I'm currently studying Prodigy IA3 LOKR but for now you will habe to deal with this adafactor optimizers.

items.name: Color-enhancer
items.description:
Model Introduction:

This model can adjust the color saturation and color-related details of images. Negative adjustments can reduce color saturation and related details, while positive adjustments enhance color saturation and relevant details. The model performs better for natural landscapes. Please feel free to send images for tweaking.

Generation Suggestions:

Suitable for all types of models, not limited to realism-focused models.

Recommended weight range: -1 to 1

Author uses high-quality restoration method: 4x_NMKD-Siax_200k

Author uses sampling method: DPM++ 2M Karras

No trigger words needed

模型简介：本模型可以调节图片的色彩饱和度以及与色彩相关的细节， 负向调整可降低色彩饱和度及相关细节，正向调整增强色彩饱和度和相关细节。该模型在自然景观方面表现更优秀。欢迎返图，喜欢请多多返图。

生成建议：

适合各种模型，不限于真实系模型。

推荐权重范围：-1~1

作者使用高清修复方法：4x_NMKD-Siax_200k

作者使用采样方法：DPM++ 2M Karras

无须触发词

注：本模型禁止用于融合，转载须经本人同意。

作者邮箱：wxs_insist@163.com

(masterpiece:1.2), best quality,PIXIV,
duck, reflection,reflective water，

items.name: Vienna Style
items.description:
About

A style for generating Baroque style pictures. This was put together using the Embedding Inspector addon. I combined tokens for different artistic styles in weightings that worked form. This style doesn't do anything special, other than guide your checkpoint to a horror themed result.

If you're an experienced prompt crafter, you probably don't need this, and could generate similar results with out it.

Installation

Place in the directory where you keep your embeddings

Usage

Use style-vienna in your prompt. Placement location in the prompt matters with this one. . Placement at the end of the prompt will give you more visual flexibility. Experiment with placing it at the beginning, middle or end of your prompt,

Depending on the LoRA or embedding used, generated images tend to be on the provocative side, use appropriate negative prompts to limit that if wish. I prefer to use checkpoints that artistic style baked in, using Photorealist models tends to produce images that look like Renaissance Faire or cosplay.

(No living artists were harmed in the making this style)

items.name: Anime Illust Diffusion XL
items.description:
模型介绍（Chinese Part）

I 引言

在本介绍中，您将了解：

  1. 模型介绍（见 II 部分）；

  2. 使用指南（见 III 部分）；

  3. 训练参数（见 IV 部分）；

  4. 触发词列表（见附录 A 部分）

II 模型介绍

动漫插画设计XL，或称 AIDXL 是一款专用于生成二次元插图的模型。它内置了 200 种以上（随着更新越来越多）的插画风格，依靠特定触发词（见附录 A 部分）触发。

优点：构图大胆，没有摆拍感，主体突出，没有过多繁杂的细节，认识很多动漫人物（依靠角色日文名拼音触发，例如，“ayanami rei”对应角色“绫波丽”，“kamado nezuko”对应角色“祢豆子”）。

模型难度较大，不推荐入门者使用。

III 使用指南（将与时俱进）

推荐使用 ComfyUI 生成图像。工作流参数如图 1 所示。

图1：ComfUI 工作流

1 提示词书写

如您所见，SDXL 的正负面提示词都分为 text_g 和 text_l 两个部分。假设您用于生成图像的描述提示词为 {main_prompt}（不包含质量描述语），质量提示词为 {quality_prompt}，负面提示次为 {neg_prompt}。则就经验来说，正面提示词的 text_g 处填写 “{main_prompt}”，text_l 处填写 “{quality_prompt}, {main_prompt}”；负面提示次的 text_g 和 text_l 都填写 “{neg_prompt}”。

另外，为了强调生成图像的风格，风格触发词的位置应尽量提前，例如， by xxx, 1girl, solo。

1.1 示例

质量提示词示例： a masterpiece with best quality, detailed 4k illustration

负面提示次示例： (low quality:1.4), bad anatomy, worst quality, ugly, disgusting, fused hands and fingers, bad hands, deformed hands and fingers, blurry, lowres, malformed, morbid, overexposure, too colorful and over-saturated, chromatic aberration, jagged

1.2 工作流

我在 Suggested Resources 内添加了 ComfyUI 的工作流 json 文件。

2 生成参数

如果您无法生成与预览图相似的图像，请参照以下指南。

  1. 建议图像总分辨率（总分辨率=高度x宽度）大于 1024x1024 且 小于 1024x1024x1.5，否则生成的图像可能质量不高。此为经验法则，即生成图像的总分辨率应高于训练集图像的总分辨率，且同时低于训练集图像总分辨率的 1.5 倍，以防止模糊和畸变。例如，本模型在 1024x1024 总分辨率上训练，因此您最大可以生成 1024x1536（以 2:3 为例）分辨率的图像。

  2. 不进行“Clip Skip”操作。

  3. 采用 “dpmpp_2m” 采样器（sampler），搭配 “karras” 调度器（scheduler），该组合在 webui 里称为 DPM++ 2M Karras。在 8 CFG 上采样 50 步。

  4. 所有涉及图像宽度（width）和高度（height）的参数均应保持一致，即所有宽度一致，所有高度一致。

  5. 仅使用模型本身，而不使用精炼器（Refiner）。

  6. 使用基底模型 vae。

  7. 使用附录部分提供的触发词以活用风格化。在未使用风格化的情况下生成图像的质量将参差不齐。

  8. 使用 SDXL 支持的 VAE 模型、文本嵌入（embeddings）模型和 Lora 模型。注意：sd-vae-ft-mse-original 不是支持 SDXL 的 vae；EasyNegative、badhandv4 等负面文本嵌入也不是支持 SDXL 的 embeddings。

IV 训练参数

以 SDXL1.0 为底模，使用大约 2w 张自己标注的图像在 5e-6 学习率，总长为 1 的余弦调度器上训练了约 100 期得到模型 A。之后在 2e-7 学习率，其余参数相同的条件下，训练得到模型 B。将模型 A 与 B 混合后得到 AIDXLv0.1 模型。

V 对比基于 SD1.5 的 AID

2023/08/08：AIDXL 使用与 AIDv2.10 完全相同的训练集进行训练，但表现优于 AIDv2.10。AIDXL 更聪明，能做到很多以 SD1.5 为底模型无法做到的事。它还能很好地区分不同概念，学习图像细节，处理对 SD1.5 来说难于登天的构图，几近完美地学习旧版 AID 无法完全掌握的风格。总的来说，它绝对拥有比 SD1.5 更高的上限，我会继续更新 AIDXL。

Model Introduction (英文部分)

I Introduction

In this introduction, you'll learn about:

Model presentation (see Section II);

Instructions for use (see Section III);

Training parameters (see Section IV);

List of Trigger Words (see Appendix Part A)

II AIDXL

Anime Illustration Design XL, or AIDXL, is a model dedicated to generating anime illustrations. It has more than 200 (with more and more updates) built-in illustration styles, which are triggered by specific trigger words (see Appendix A).

Advantages: flexible composition, no sense of posing, prominent subject, not too many complicated details, familiar with many anime characters (triggered by the character's name, for example, "ayanami rei" corresponds to the character "Ayanami Rei", "kamado nezuko " corresponds to the character "Nezuko", "lucy \(cyberpunk edgerunners\) corresponds to the character "Lucy").

It's a little bit difficult. Not recommended for beginners.

III User Guide

(Keep pace with the times)

It is recommended to use ComfyUI to generate images rather than WebUI for higher generation speed, flexibility and even image quality. The workflow parameters are shown in Figure 1.

Figure 1: ComfUI workflow

1 Guidance of Prompt Writing

As you can see, SDXL Clip has both positive and negative prompts divided into two parts, text_g and text_l. Assume that the description prompt you use to generate images is {main_prompt} (without the quality prompt), the quality prompt is {quality_prompt}, and the negative prompt is {neg_prompt}. The rule of thumb is, for positive prompts, filling in “{main_prompt}” in text_g, and “{quality_prompt}, {main_prompt}” in text_l. For negative prompts, filling in “{neg_prompt}” in both text_g and text_l.

In addition, in order to emphasize the style of the generated image, the position of the style trigger word should be as early as possible, or even be the first tag. For example, by yoneyama mai, 1girl, solo.

1.1 Examples

Quality prompts: a masterpiece with best quality, detailed 4k illustration

Negative prompts: (low quality:1.4), bad anatomy, worst quality, ugly, disgusting, fused hands and fingers, bad hands, deformed hands and fingers, blurry, lowres, malformed, morbid, overexposure, too colorful and over- saturated, chromatic aberration, jagged

1.2 Workflow

I added ComfyUI's workflow json file inside the suggested resources tab.

2 Suggested Generation Parameters

If you are unable to generate an image similar to the preview, please follow the guidelines below.

  1. It is recommended that the total image resolution (total resolution = height x width) be greater than 1024x1024 and less than 1024x1024x1.5, otherwise the generated image may not be of high quality. This is a rule of thumb that the total resolution of the generated images should be higher than the total resolution of the training set images and at the same time lower than 1.5 times the total resolution of the training set images to prevent blurring and distortion. For example, this model is trained on a total resolution of 1024x1024, so you can generate images up to a resolution of 1024x1536 (2:3 for example).

  2. Do not skip clip layers.

  3. Use "dpmpp_2m" sampler (sampler), with "karras" scheduler (scheduler), this combination is called DPM++ 2M Karras in webui. Sample 50 steps over 8 CFG.

  4. All parameters related to image width and height should be consistent, that is, all widths are the same, and all heights are the same.

  5. Do not use refiner model.

  6. Use VAE of the model itself.

  7. Use the trigger words provided in the appendix to apply specific style(s). You can merge styles to get amazing results. The quality of the resulting images without stylization will vary.

  8. Use SDXL supported VAE models, text embeddings (embeddings) models and Lora models. Note: sd-vae-ft-mse-original is not an SDXL-capable vae; negative embeddings like EasyNegative and badhandv4 are not SDXL-capable embeddings.

IV Training Parameters

Using SDXL1.0 as the base model, using about 22k labeled images to train about 100 epochs on a cosine scheduler with a learning rate of 5e-6 and a total length of 1 to obtain model A. Then, using a learning rate of 2e-7 and the same other parameters to obtain model B. The AIDXLv0.1 model is obtained by merging model A and B.

V AIDXL vs SD1.5 based AID

2023/08/08. AIDXL is trained on the same training set as AIDv2.10, but outperforms AIDv2.10. AIDXL is smarter and can do many things that SD1.5-based models cannot. It also does a really good job of distinguishing between concepts, learning image detail, handling compositions that are difficult or even impossible for SD1.5 and AID. Overall, it is absolute potential. I'll keep updating AIDXL.

海南鱼茶Hainan Yucha (Originally: 海南鱼鲊Hainan Yuzha. 鲊Zha means pickled fish.)

A kind of fermented foods from Hainan Province, China.

Because of its smell, it is one of the several foods called "Chinese canned herring".

Rice, raw fish, and Jiuqu(Fermentation starter) are put into jars and fermented for about 25 days.

Depending on the method, the degree of fermentation can be judged by the maggots growing in it.

This is similar to the most original Japanese sushi.

海南鱼茶（原始称法应是海南鱼鲊，鲊指腌鱼）

一种来自中国海南省的发酵食物。

因为其臭味，是数种被叫做“中国的鲱鱼罐头”的食品之一。

米、生鱼肉、九曲放入广口瓶中，发酵大约25天。

根据方法不同，可以通过其中生长的蛆来判断发酵程度。

这类似于最原始的日本寿司。

Welcome to Neonify SDXL! This STYLE LoRa will Cartoonerize your prompts add Neon Realism to the image. This STYLE LoRa is specifically trained on Neon Realism and Cel-Shaded gamelike graphics with a Retro-Cyber vibe . 1900 images tokened with trigger word "Neon Realism" for SDXL only.

Style Format: Lora Weight + Trigger Word + Color

Example Prompt: <lora:Neonify:0.50>, neon realism, (light blue and light amber)

Please read the following instructions to properly activate the Style!!!

1. There are 3 components to the activating the style.

- Choosing the Neonify LoRa and LoRa Weight (recommended is 0.50 to start and try with the Original LoRa)

- Trigger word = "Neon Realism"

- Adding a Color theme = Blue, red, amber, colorful, etc. (this is optional)

2. Depending on your application and needs, I have provided LoRas with increasing strengths training.

Neonify Original - 35k steps (Try this one first)

Neonify V2 Lite - 75k Steps (This one also good standalone)

Neonify V2 Med - 150k Steps

Neonify V2 Intense - 225k Steps

Neonify V2 Extreme - 300k Steps (For use potentially with other LoRas)

The Extreme for example, it is easier to achieve the Game-Like Retro-Cyber look without using the Neon Realism trigger words as it will bleed through the training images. However, this is only necessary if you are using multiple LoRas and need to have this style to be strong and mixed in at a lower weight.

3. Finally, if you got anything out of this LoRa, please upload a picture of your result. I would GREATLY appreciate your feedback.

items.name: 相约98/1990s animation style Lora
items.description:
来吧 来吧 相约九八，来吧 来吧 相约一九九八。

相约在甜美的春风里，相约那永远的青春年华。

大家好，我是chosen鲷，这次给大家带来的是90年代画风lora。

说是90年代画风其实有点不准确，实际上从1983年的猫眼三姐妹那时候业界就已经是很成熟的画风了，到了90年代的Eva，柯南（早期）之类的其实都是一脉相承的赛璐璐画风，即使用赛璐璐胶片去叠化上色拍摄的技法。随着步入千禧年，电脑这个玩意开始普及，动画的制作也渐渐地走向了数字化，这种特有的画风也逐渐消失了，直到2013年，最后一部赛璐璐动画转为数字制作，从此消声绝迹。这也是为什么我给这个lora起名为“相约98”，如果你也喜欢这种画风，那就让我们重回到千禧年之前，一起相约98吧！

值得一提的是这个不是只能画二次元，也可以做偏写实风格，会有一种早期港风明星的感觉，搭配majic即可，建议使用lora分层，后三层全设置为0即可。推荐的权重0.8-1.0

推荐的tag：

(masterpiece:1.2), best quality,PIXIV, style of a 1990s anime,

<lora:s_20230805204449:0.8>

大模型方面，我的impasto ，chosen mix都行，还有ghost也很好，写实类的majic系的就可以，其他的常见模型也都行。
